      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、遙子さん",
      "startTime": 2.5333332221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei001.wav",
      "text": "お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 4.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あら、大きな紙袋を両手一杯に抱えてどうしたの？",
      "startTime": 5.6836052736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk001.wav",
      "text": "もしかして……それ全部、バレンタインのチョコ？",
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "学校帰りに校門の前で後輩の子達に囲まれて、次々に",
      "startTime": 17.7892518203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei002.wav",
      "text": "チョコを渡されたんです。人数が多くて大変でした",
      "startTime": 23.068845624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "女子校は美人で格好いい先輩が人気があるって言うよな",
      "startTime": 28.3519273599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh001.wav",
      "text": "怜は後輩達にとって憧れの格好いい先輩ってことか",
      "startTime": 33.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恥ずかしいから、あんまり茶化さないで下さい",
      "startTime": 38.5011332672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei003.wav",
      "text": "それより、さくら達はまだ来てないんですか？",
      "startTime": 42.6276418367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくら達ならまだ学校のはずだ",
      "startTime": 46.1343757471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh002.wav",
      "text": "とりあえず全員揃うまでお茶でも飲んで待っていてくれ",
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうそう、美味しいケーキを買ってあるんだ。俺と",
      "startTime": 53.032811308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh003.wav",
      "text": "たわいもない世間話でもしながら一緒に食べないか？",
      "startTime": 56.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます……",
      "startTime": 60.9761221092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei004.wav",
      "text": "急にケーキなんて、どうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 64.8888438858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "別に他意はないよ。なんとなく今日はみんなと",
      "startTime": 68.364194568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh004.wav",
      "text": "お喋りしたい気分なんだ。本当にそれだけだから",
      "startTime": 72.0205072087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それにしても、今日はバレンタインかー。好きな人に",
      "startTime": 76.116548745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh005.wav",
      "text": "チョコを贈る日かー。みんなはどうするのかなー",
      "startTime": 81.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふっ。ねぇ、もしかして、私達が誰にチョコを",
      "startTime": 87.5936047078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk002.wav",
      "text": "渡すのか気になって、探りを入れてるのかしら？",
      "startTime": 92.6121342342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いえ、別に、みんなが誰に本命チョコをあげるのか",
      "startTime": 96.8177769821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh006.wav",
      "text": "気になってるとかそんなんじゃ全然なくて……全然……",
      "startTime": 100.000004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁぁぁぁぁ……すみません、物凄く気になってます",
      "startTime": 104.40278821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh007.wav",
      "text": "変な人に騙されていないか、気が気じゃなくて……",
      "startTime": 111.600004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}君、心配性な保護者みたいね",
      "startTime": 115.6837407272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk003.wav",
      "text": "大丈夫よ。相手はちゃんとした人だから",
      "startTime": 120.2201398214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やっぱり、遙子さんはみんなが誰に本命チョコを",
      "startTime": 124.187799724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh008.wav",
      "text": "渡すか知っているんですね！",
      "startTime": 127.1333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恋愛をするなとは言いません。ただ、アイドルに",
      "startTime": 129.2557589372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh009.wav",
      "text": "恋人がいるなんて噂になったら大事ですから",
      "startTime": 132.4333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事務所としても、マネージャーとしても、備えだけは",
      "startTime": 135.9053731442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh010.wav",
      "text": "しておきたいんです。だから教えてもらえませんか？",
      "startTime": 139.300004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk004.wav",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。今は教える訳にはいかないのよ",
      "startTime": 143.8937628588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですか……分かりました……。ああ、でも気になる",
      "startTime": 148.3024248761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh011.wav",
      "text": "みんなが本命チョコを渡す相手は一体どんな人なんだ",
      "startTime": 154.700004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に気付いてないんですね……。ところで、そこの",
      "startTime": 158.8229235015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei005.wav",
      "text": "段ボール箱の山はファンから届いたチョコですよね？",
      "startTime": 165.0012465469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この量を抱えて帰るのはさすがに無理なので",
      "startTime": 169.012878005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei006.wav",
      "text": "イベントが終わった後に寮まで運んでもらえますか？",
      "startTime": 172.9679132136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "イベントまで日にちがあるし",
      "startTime": 176.8209960304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-koh012.wav",
      "text": "別に今日運んでも構わないが……",
      "startTime": 179.3356801346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいえ、イベントの後でお願いします",
      "startTime": 182.6983625097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-rei007.wav",
      "text": "その日なら、みんなも寮にいるはずなので",
      "startTime": 186.2550076317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうそう、必ず{user}君が",
      "startTime": 189.5498816492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_03-hrk005.wav",
      "text": "寮に持って来てね。みんなで待ってるわ",
      "startTime": 192.2757395429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
